title: Images: Chicago Cubs finish off St. Louis Cardinals with a 6-4 win in game four of the Division Series
text:
See images from the Chicago Cubs' 6-4 Division Series-clinching win over the St. Louis Cardinals at Wrigley Field in Chicago Tuesday. The Cubs advance to face the Mets or Dodgers on Saturday to begin the National League Championship Series. Related Article
